<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Order Shipped</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; }
        strong { color: #0056b3; }
        .order-number { font-weight: bold; color: black; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Good news! Your order has shipped!</h1>
    <p>Your order <span class="order-number">#{{.OrderNumber}}</span> is on its way to you.</p>
    <p>
        Tracking Number: <strong>{{.TrackingNumber}}</strong>
    </p>
    <p>
        Estimated Delivery Date: <strong>{{.EstimatedDeliveryDate | formatAsDate}}</strong>
    </p>
    <p>You can use the tracking number on the carrier's website to follow your package's journey.</p>
</body>
</html>